OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,FA breast surgeon who carried out
OL,7,Funapproved mastectomies was a
OL,8,F"nightmare" to work with, a former
OL,9,Fcolleague has told an inquest into the
OL,10,Fdeath of one of his cancer patients.
OL,12,FIan Paterson, who worked in
OL,13,FBirmingham, is currently serving a 20-
OL,14,Fyear jail sentence after being
OL,15,Fconvicted of 17 counts of wounding
OL,16,Fwith intent and three counts of
OL,17,Funlawful wounding in 2017.
