OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,FHe performed unauthorised "cleavage-
OL,7,Fsparing" mastectomies, which left
OL,8,Fbehind breast tissue for cosmetic
OL,9,Freasons but increased the risk of
OL,10,Fcancer returning.
OL,12,FFormer breast cancer patients Chloe
OL,13,FNikitas, 43, whose judge-led inquest
OL,14,Flast week was the first of 62 to be
OL,15,Fheard at Birmingham and Solihull
OL,16,FCoroners Court over the next eight
OL,17,Fmonths, and Elaine Turbill, 63, whose
OL,18,Finquest is being held this week, were
OL,19,Fsubjected to cleavage-sparing
OL,20,Fmastectomies by Paterson and both
OL,21,Flater died of metastatic cancer.
