OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,FGiving evidence on Wednesday at Mrs
OL,7,FTurbill's inquest, Paterson's former
OL,8,Fcolleague and consultant radiologist
OL,9,Fat Solihull Hospital, Dr Chris
OL,10,FFletcher, said the pair had a "frosty"
OL,11,Frelationship at times.
OL,13,FHe told the inquest they had worked
OL,14,Ftogether between 1998 and 2011 and
OL,15,Fthat reviewing mammograms from
OL,16,FPaterson's patients made up at least
OL,17,F"90%" of his workload at both the NHS
OL,18,Fand privately at Spire hospitals.
OL,20,F"He always tried to run the show"
