OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,FDr Fletcher said their relationship
OL,7,Fwas "complex" and "difficult" because
OL,8,Fof the way Paterson worked and he
OL,9,Fended up making a complaint about him.
OL,11,FHe said: "He was a nightmare. He was
OL,12,Fquite aggressive and quite demanding
OL,13,Fin a way I had never come across
OL,14,Fbefore.
OL,16,F"At a time where he was ingratiating
OL,17,Fhimself with me, you almost felt he
OL,18,Fwas using flattery to get you to do
OL,19,Fthings. Then it became rocky again."
