OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,FDr Fletcher said their relationship
OL,7,Fdeteriorated further after he signed a
OL,8,Fletter, alongside other colleagues,
OL,9,Fraising concerns about Paterson.
OL,11,FHe said: "After 2007, when I 'sided
OL,12,Fwith the enemy' as he saw it, we had a
OL,13,Fvery frosty relationship after that
OL,14,Fand he only spoke to me when he had
OL,15,Fto. He was very difficult to work
OL,16,Fwith."
OL,18,F"There was a tumour and he had missed
OL,19,Fit"
