OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,F"We were all a bit shellshocked and
OL,7,Fembarrassed by that. Nobody ever
OL,8,Fflagged it as perhaps it should have
OL,9,Fbeen flagged."
OL,11,FPaterson has agreed to give evidence
OL,12,Fremotely from prison at Mrs Turbill's
OL,13,Finquest on Thursday.
OL,15,FCoroner Richard Foster said Paterson
OL,16,Fhas requested he only give oral
OL,17,Fevidence one day a week so as to
OL,18,F"minimise disruption to his prison
OL,19,Fregime".
