OL,3,CBreast surgeon was 'nightmare' to work
OL,4,Cwith, former colleague tells inquest
OL,6,FJudge Foster said: "All witnesses have
OL,7,Fhad to sacrifice aspects of their
OL,8,Fdaily lives in order to give evidence,
OL,9,Fno doubt to considerable inconvenience
OL,10,Fto themselves and their families. Many
OL,11,Fwitnesses are long since retired.
OL,13,F"In the same way, it is not
OL,14,Funreasonable to expect Mr Paterson to
OL,15,Fsacrifice aspects of his settled
OL,16,Fprison regime in order to provide
OL,17,Fevidence."
OL,19,FThe inquest continues.
